Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fscy100\c&H010102&\bord0\blur0.5\\b1\fs100\pos(644,430)}Xuyên Thấu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Acid Down. {hán}
